Description: Tools for the computation of inequality indicators in LISSY. 
  This package contains three different types of functions. 'lissyuse', 'transformation' 
   and 'output' functions. 'lissyuse' allows users to read LIS and LWS data. Transformation functions add
  easy data manipulation stages to LISSY jobs. Output functions help users to print aggregated figures and
  plots for their tasks.
